longBusinessSummary: Sky Constant Century Inc. provides precious metals spot contract trading services for gold and silver trading through electronic trading platform located in Hong Kong. The company was formerly known as eBullion, Inc. and changed its name to Sky Constant Century Inc. in August 2023. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is based in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong.
